body:
The Avicus Staff Summer Survey is a super fun creation by yours truly, Acceqted. It's a cool way to bond staff members and members together. I will set a date in the future in which I will go on team speak and announce the winner of each category. There will possibly be a prize, so stay tuned.

How will it work?

Down below I will post a link to a google forms survey. There, you will easily click on the link, properly fill out the form. And wait until the final date, in which I will reveal the answer. If anyone is interested in helping out, you can contact me and Skype at "hovdoge". this includes all staff [Referee's, Officials, TS Developers and Media team members.] You may use the same staff member over and over again, but the more you differentiate, the better the outcome will be.

The Magical Link


http://goo.gl/forms/tODM6U6PcQqkRn4f2

Link to staff page

https://avicus.net/staff

The Date When Results Will Be Released                                          


IN AN HOUR! TELL EVERYONE!
